John W. Eaves 
Executive Compensation
As Chief Executive Officer at ARCH COAL INC, John W. Eaves  made $12,797,344 in total compensation.  Of this total $1,025,000 was received as a salary, $1,494,361 was received as a bonus, $0 was received in stock options, $10,237,770 was awarded as stock and $40,213 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


