Background

		Mr. John W. Eaves, also known as Jo, has been Chief Executive Officer of Arch Coal, Inc. since April  26, 2012. Mr. Eaves served as President of Arch Coal Inc since April 28, 2006 until April 23, 2015. He served as the Chief Operating Officer at Arch Coal Inc. since December 2002 until April 26, 2012. Mr. Eaves joined Arch Coal Inc. in 1987 and served as its Executive Vice President from December 2002 to April 28, 2006. From February 2000 to December 2002, he served ... as the Senior Vice President of Marketing at Arch Coal Inc. and from September 1995 to December 2002 as President of its subsidiary, Arch Coal Sales Company Inc. Mr. Eaves served as the Vice President of Marketing at Arch Coal Inc. from July 1997 to February 2000. He served in various capacities with Diamond Shamrock, Arch's predecessor and Natomas Coal. Mr. Eaves served as Chairman of the Board at Arch Coal Inc. since April 23, 2015 until October 7, 2016. Mr. Eaves served as a Vice Chairman of ADA-ES Inc., until November 10, 2011  and also served as its Interim Vice Chairman since March 2006. Mr. Eaves has been a Director at Arch Coal Inc. since February 23, 2006. Mr. Eaves has been a Director of CoaLogix Inc. since July 2009. He served as a Director of ADA-ES Inc., from October 2003 to November 10, 2011. Mr. Eaves holds a B.S. from the University of Kentucky and completed the Executive Management program at the Wharton School of the University of Pennsylvania and the Advanced Management Program at Harvard Business School.Read Full Background




